data.description: Have you ever wanted to live in a finebuilders home? Well your time has come! Every surface has been updated and given that professional attention. This 2 bed 1.5 bath home is in immaculate condition with new siding, new windows, new laminate floors, Gorgeous New Kitchen with  subway tiles and marble tiles on the island, new stainless appliances and a large walk in pantry.  The outside is unparalleled in patio living, trellis's, potted plants, color at every turn...there are two shed's a "she-shed and a he-shed!" Along with a large oversized 1 car garage with tons of shelving for storage and room for a shop. Great parking inside and out, wood shed will include 1 cord dry wood. All heated by a wood fireplace, or forced air heat system.
